Class RedCell

    • main.cell.Cell

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Locatable

    public class RedCell
extends Cell
    An implementation of the abstract cell. This cell is neutral to the player. It starts out at a health of a 100. These cells are conquerable nodes by the player.
